  "description": "SCURRY macro drives rapid oscillator instability that makes held notes feel like short, nervous runs. The possum crossing open ground in a hurry — no time to pause, each footfall a slightly different weight. Weight oscillator at half-octave tuning creates an involuntary countermelody. BITE controlled — this is urgency, not aggression.",
